      "utterance": "对，VoteMessage绑定Retail_Inventory。接下来需要SignedVoteMessage表示签名后的投票，这个关系到客户忠诚度系统Retail_CustomerLoyalty，因为签名涉及用户身份验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SignedVoteMessage",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "VoteMessage"
